---
title: Double Asian Popcorn Chicken & Garlic Rice with Oyster Sauce Veggies & Sesame Dressing
description: Pan-fried chicken and stir-fried veggies; it’s almost too good to be true. Cook the veggies in a umami oyster sauce and sprinkle chicken in a delicious seasoning. This will help to give it a signature golden glow. Even the rice has an extra kick of flavour from the garlic. This dinner really is a dream come true!
